    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i tried the bedding procedure like you said but the squeal is still there and it honestly sounds so weird... like it's coming from deep inside the wheel well. it's such an erratic, sudden noise. do you think it could be something loose or bouncing around in there, or maybe a piece of debris caught in the brake shield?",
